{"lemma":"عِبْرِيٌّ","slug":"عِبْرِيٌّ","root":"ع.ب.ر","root_slug":"ع-ب-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-ب-ر","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["adj","noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n27834","n27835"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%90%D8%A8%D9%92%D8%B1%D9%90%D9%8A%D9%8C%D9%91"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"Hebrew, Hebraic"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"Hebrew (language)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a Hebrew"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"the Hebrew language","tags":["colloquial"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From Hebrew עִבְרִי ('ivrí, ʿiḇrī). Related to the root ع ب ر (ʕ b r)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n27834","headword_ar":"عُبْرِىٌّ","root":"Ebr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", applied to the [species of lote-tree called]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sidor","text_ar":"سِدْر"},{"kind":"text","text":", means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"That grows on the banks of rivers, and becomes large:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O:) an anomalous rel. n. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiborN","text_ar":"عِبْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) [or a regular rel. n. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuborN","text_ar":"عُبْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiborN","text_ar":"عِبْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":] or, accord. to 'Omárah,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as is large in the leaves, having few thorns, and taller than the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaAl","text_ar":"ضَال"},{"kind":"text","text":": or, as Aboo-Ziyád says,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that has no thorns except such as hurt"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sidorN","text_ar":"سِدْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":")]; the thorns [that hurt] being of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sidor","text_ar":"سِدْر"},{"kind":"text","text":"called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DAl","text_ar":"ضال"},{"kind":"text","text":": he does not say, as others do, that it is that which grows upon the water: some assert that"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it is also called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EumoriY~N","text_ar":"عُمْرِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"b","text_ar":"ب"},{"kind":"text","text":"being changed into"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"m","text_ar":"م"},{"kind":"text","text":": (O:) or, as some say,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as has no trunk; and such is only of those that are near to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eibor","text_ar":"عِبْر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bank of a river"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: Yaakoob says that the terms"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuboriY~","text_ar":"عُبْرِىّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EumoriY~","text_ar":"عُمْرِىّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"are applied to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sidor","text_ar":"سِدْر"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that imbibes water;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and that such as does not this is that of the desert, and is the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DAl","text_ar":"ضال"},{"kind":"text","text":": AZ says that the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sdr","text_ar":"سدر"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as is large"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eawosaj","text_ar":"عَوْسَج"},{"kind":"text","text":", are called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuboriY~N","text_ar":"عُبْرِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EumoriY~N","text_ar":"عُمْرِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is applied to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sdr","text_ar":"سدر"},{"kind":"text","text":"that is old. (TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EumoriY~N","text_ar":"عُمْرِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["S","O","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n27835","headword_ar":"عِبْرِىٌّ","root":"Ebr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Hebrew:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a Hebrew"},{"kind":"text","text":"]."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEiboriy~uwna","text_ar":"العِبْرِيُّونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is an appellation of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The Jews"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the Hebrews"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (O.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEiboriY~u","text_ar":"العِبْرِىُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEiboraAniY~u","text_ar":"العِبْرَانِىُّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEiboriy~apu","text_ar":"العِبْرِيَّةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEiboraAniy~apu","text_ar":"العِبْرَانِيَّةُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, TA,) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The Hebrew language;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the language of the Jews."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, O, K, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","A","K","O","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}